      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROCK REVOLUTION (3) led and was quickly back on track, narrowly beaten over 1600m in stronger. Draws low and has a handy 2kg claim today. Ready to win. MAXXI BON (2) drifted well back in the same contest before winding up strongly to miss a whisker. Carries more weight but will be finishing hard again. ROSSANADO (4) comes out of the same race and bounced straight into a handy position from the inside draw, beaten less than 1L. Solid top-three prospects. VANGUARD LEGEND (1) resumed in good order but was plain over 1200m in this grade following. Was a comfortable winner at his only start over a mile, and with the extra fitness, a much better effort is on the cards.",
